    <body>
      <section eId="sec_1836_C">
        <num>1836-C</num>
        <heading>Applications for loans</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_1836_C__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the history and membership of the association;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1836_C__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the history and circumstances of the plant to be acquired;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1836_C__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>financial and marketing projections and analyses sufficient to\nallow the authority to evaluate the continued economic viability of the\nproject;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1836_C__subsec_d">
          <num>(d)</num>
          <content>
            <p>estimate of the number of jobs to be saved or created by the\nproject; and\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1836_C__subsec_e">
          <num>(e)</num>
          <content>
            <p>total anticipated project cost.\n  2. The application shall also include a detailed financial statement\nof funding partner participation in the project, which shall include:\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1836_C__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the identity of all funding partners; and\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1836_C__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the terms of the financing agreements with the funding partners,\nincluding any repayment schedules and finance charges to be included in\nsuch agreements.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
